1
00:00:39,960 --> 00:00:41,399
Bro, the moment you left,

2
00:00:41,719 --> 00:00:43,039
someone showed up to stir up trouble.

3
00:00:45,200 --> 00:00:48,560
Could someone be mixed in with them, instigating?

4
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:50,119
Take a good look.

5
00:00:50,679 --> 00:00:52,520
Don't end up going to prison

6
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:54,719
without even knowing why.

7
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:56,079
Go to prison?

8
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:57,560
Could it be her?

9
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:21,680
Lili, Lili.

10
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:23,560
Aunt Zhang.

11
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:24,200
What's up?

12
00:01:24,359 --> 00:01:25,480
Is Yihai here?

13
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:27,680
No, Bro Hai went out on business.

14
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:28,400
Let me tell you,

15
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:30,560
Another family on Aimin Street had trouble.

16
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,359
Did you know?

17
00:01:31,359 --> 00:01:32,200
Really?

18
00:01:32,439 --> 00:01:33,319
I know.

19
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:35,319
Wasn't it carbon monoxide poisoning?

20
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:36,319
Let me tell you,

21
00:01:36,319 --> 00:01:37,519
last night there was someone

22
00:01:37,799 --> 00:01:38,959
sneaking around suspiciously.

23
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,799
I told Section Chief Dao,

24
00:01:40,799 --> 00:01:42,319
but he said I was seeing things.

25
00:01:43,799 --> 00:01:44,239
Alright.

26
00:01:44,239 --> 00:01:45,159
Aunt Zhang, got it.

27
00:01:45,359 --> 00:01:46,680
I'll tell Bro Hai when he gets back.

28
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:48,280
Okay, thank you in advance.

29
00:01:48,439 --> 00:01:50,400
Aimin Street's business is Bro Hai's.

30
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:52,200
We always end up bothering you.

31
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:52,799
Thanks again, really.

32
00:01:52,799 --> 00:01:53,519
No problem.

33
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:54,519
I'm off then.

34
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,799
Take care, Aunt Zhang.

35
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:56,680
Okay.

36
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:02,519
Where's Director Ge?

37
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,519
I'm the one looking for you.

38
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:07,640
What's going on?

39
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:09,759
Out with it.

40
00:02:10,319 --> 00:02:11,199
What's the deal?

41
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,479
What do you mean, "what's the deal"?

42
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:14,560
This month,

43
00:02:14,879 --> 00:02:16,639
there've been so many accidents.

44
00:02:17,039 --> 00:02:17,680
Is it a lot?

45
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,400
Isn't it?

46
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,719
Over a dozen in one month.

47
00:02:20,719 --> 00:02:22,400
Didn't you say they were accidents?

48
00:02:22,639 --> 00:02:23,840
Gas tank leaks,

49
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:25,199
carbon monoxide poisoning,

50
00:02:25,199 --> 00:02:26,240
elderly people getting electrocuted.

51
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:27,680
Don't worry.

52
00:02:27,879 --> 00:02:29,120
We've already increased manpower

53
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,599
and educated them on safety.

54
00:02:30,599 --> 00:02:31,840
All happened this month.

55
00:02:32,039 --> 00:02:32,919
Just a coincidence, right?

56
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,159
Coincidence?

57
00:02:34,159 --> 00:02:35,680
And all concentrated on Aimin Street.

58
00:02:40,319 --> 00:02:41,759
Are you saying

59
00:02:42,039 --> 00:02:42,919
someone did it on purpose?

60
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,639
What I'm saying is,

61
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:46,319
shouldn't you be investigating?

62
00:02:48,919 --> 00:02:49,960
Well,

63
00:02:51,159 --> 00:02:52,479
the Security Section

64
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,960
can only act once someone files a report.

65
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:57,719
If no one files a report, we can't act.

66
00:02:59,879 --> 00:03:00,319
Fine.

67
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:02,840
I'll investigate.

68
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,759
Then I'll come file a report with you.

69
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,199
Fine.

70
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,400
Where you going?

71
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,199
Let go.

72
00:03:19,879 --> 00:03:21,479
Honey.

73
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,800
Forgive me.

74
00:03:25,719 --> 00:03:27,199
Are you a psycho?

75
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:28,520
Honey,

76
00:03:30,199 --> 00:03:31,759
forgive me.

77
00:03:31,759 --> 00:03:34,479
You can't keep hating me forever.

78
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,479
Her talk of illicit massage services...

79
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,599
So this was payback all along.

80
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,360
Looks like we got it wrong.

81
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,759
What... what nonsense are you spouting?

82
00:03:43,759 --> 00:03:45,919
The reason you still hate me

83
00:03:45,919 --> 00:03:46,840
is because

84
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:49,479
we never got to be together properly.

85
00:03:49,479 --> 00:03:50,360
Honey...

86
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,599
Stop talking nonsense.

87
00:03:51,599 --> 00:03:53,599
I never made you a promise,

88
00:03:53,599 --> 00:03:56,599
but you can't bet your future on me.

89
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:00,479
Shameless!

90
00:04:00,479 --> 00:04:01,560
I'm so shameless.

91
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,919
I'm shameless.

92
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,479
Get off!

93
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:08,240
Trying to mess with me?

94
00:04:45,879 --> 00:04:46,680
Another one, huh?

95
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,279
What are you doing here?

96
00:04:49,879 --> 00:04:50,519
Perfect timing.

97
00:04:50,759 --> 00:04:51,639
Help me chase after her.

98
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:54,519
Zhu Yihai!

99
00:04:54,519 --> 00:04:55,519
You've got some nerve!

100
00:04:55,759 --> 00:04:57,360
Using your ex-girlfriend to chase a girl?

101
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:58,279
Just hurry up!

102
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,279
It's not what you think!

103
00:05:00,839 --> 00:05:01,639
Let go of me!

104
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:47,839
Alright.

105
00:05:48,279 --> 00:05:48,959
You should head back.

106
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,360
It might be dangerous up ahead.

107
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:51,839
Dumping me now that you're done?

108
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,399
There's real danger.

109
00:05:54,439 --> 00:05:55,439
Then pay the cab fare.

110
00:05:56,839 --> 00:05:57,399
Scan the code.

111
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,160
Scan what code?

112
00:05:59,519 --> 00:05:59,959
Get lost.

113
00:06:15,399 --> 00:06:17,240
This should be the place.

114
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:47,639
Hello.

115
00:06:47,639 --> 00:06:49,079
Factory Office Secretariat.

116
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,439
Not good.

117
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,639
Hello, Factory Office.

118
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:07,839
I'm from the Factory Office Secretariat.

119
00:07:08,839 --> 00:07:10,199
Are you the one who reported

120
00:07:10,199 --> 00:07:11,360
that someone's been threatening you?

121
00:07:15,879 --> 00:07:16,519
Yeah.

122
00:07:18,519 --> 00:07:19,600
Come in and talk.

123
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,279
Okay.

124
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,600
Can't find Mom and Dad's place?

125
00:07:32,399 --> 00:07:33,199
Sorry to bother you.

126
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,480
Let's go.

127
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,040
What are you doing?

128
00:07:58,959 --> 00:07:59,759
Come on, let's go.

129
00:08:00,319 --> 00:08:01,439
Mom and Dad already cooked dinner.

130
00:08:01,439 --> 00:08:02,240
They can't wait.

131
00:08:02,639 --> 00:08:03,800
Show some respect.

132
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,120
I'm trying to save you, you know that?

133
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,720
You think I'd believe your bullshit?

134
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:10,839
See for yourself.

135
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,720
Where are you going?

136
00:08:17,079 --> 00:08:17,680
To save someone.

137
00:08:17,879 --> 00:08:19,639
Are you crazy? You'll get yourself killed!

138
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:21,160
Look at all that's happened lately.

139
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,720
This guy's definitely behind it all.

140
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:23,639
Look.

141
00:08:30,959 --> 00:08:33,039
How could this be related to Long Xiao?

142
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:34,519
How could it involve Long Xiao?

143
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,840
Like you don't know.

144
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:37,120
You two are thick as thieves.

145
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:39,080
I really don't know about this.

146
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,559
You think I'm an idiot?

147
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:41,679
Aren't you?

148
00:08:41,759 --> 00:08:42,080
You...

149
00:08:42,639 --> 00:08:43,440
Zhu Yihai.

150
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:47,279
That doesn't add up.

151
00:08:48,399 --> 00:08:51,399
Director Ge already signed the contract.

152
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:54,039
Why would Long Xiao do this?

153
00:08:55,159 --> 00:08:56,159
You think Long Xiao

154
00:08:56,159 --> 00:08:58,000
would let you have a sure thing?

155
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,679
You're so easygoing.

156
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,000
You say he owes you money,

157
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,159
yet you're not the least bit worried.

158
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,759
He... he owes me money.

159
00:09:07,519 --> 00:09:08,759
I'll lend you some men

160
00:09:08,759 --> 00:09:09,759
to force him into submission.

161
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:12,360
We just need him to sign this agreement.

162
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:13,840
If he fires people again,

163
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:16,159
won't that prove

164
00:09:16,799 --> 00:09:18,519
everything I just said is true?

165
00:09:20,919 --> 00:09:22,639
So he's been using me this whole time.

166
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:26,000
Now you know who the idiot is, huh?

167
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,200
You stay right here.

168
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,000
I'm going to find some men.

169
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:40,320
Don't go anywhere.

170
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:03,759
Hello.

171
00:10:05,039 --> 00:10:06,080
I've been exposed.

172
00:10:06,519 --> 00:10:07,440
Need a cleanup.

173
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:09,320
Tie up the loose ends.

174
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,080
Leave no trace.

175
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:11,879
I'll arrange for you to go to Nanyang.

